            <div class="ep-a_heading ep-layout_level3">
                <h3 class="ep_title">
                    <div class="ep-p_text"><a href="https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/headlines/world/20200624STO81906/exploring-migration-causes-why-people-migrate" title="Read more"><span class="ep_name">Exploring migration causes – why people migrate</span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span></a></div>
                </h3>
                <div class="ep_subtitle">
                    <div class="ep-p_text ep-layout_category"><span class="ep_name">World</span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span></div>
                    
                        
    <div class="ep-p_text ep-layout_date">
        <span class="ep_name">
            
    
    
        <time itemprop="datePublished"
              datetime="2020-07-01T15:37:00">01-07-2020 - 15:37</time>
    

        </span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span>
    </div>

                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ep-a_text" data-visibility750="false" data-visibility640="false" data-visibility480="false" data-visibility320="false">
                <p>People migrate for many reasons , ranging from security, demography and human rights to poverty and climate change. Find out more.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>


            

                

    <article class="ep_gridcolumn ep-m_product ep-layout_linkmode " data-view1200="3" data-view1020="3" data-view750="6" data-view640="4" data-view480="8" data-view320="4">
