                </h3>
                <div class="ep_subtitle">
                    <div class="ep-p_text ep-layout_category"><span class="ep_name">Security</span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span></div>
                    
                        
    <div class="ep-p_text ep-layout_date">
        <span class="ep_name">
            
    
    
        <time itemprop="datePublished"
              datetime="2020-06-30T14:40:00">30-06-2020 - 14:40</time>
    

        </span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span>
    </div>

                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ep-a_text" data-visibility750="false" data-visibility640="false" data-visibility480="false" data-visibility320="false">
                <p>The EU&#39;s passport-free travel space, known as the Schengen area, is one of the most tangible achievements of European integration. Learn about it in our guide.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>


            

                

