            <div class="ep-a_text" data-visibility750="false" data-visibility640="false" data-visibility480="false" data-visibility320="false">
                <p>Measures against Covid-19 are needed, but their impact on privacy and freedom must be proportionate and temporary, said  Maria Arena, the chair of the human rights subcommittee.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>


            

                

